          <h2>WEB SITE PRIVACY POLICY</h2>
          <p>
            The Internet is an amazing tool. It has the power to change the way
            we live, and we're starting to see that potential today. With only a
            few mouse-clicks, you can follow the news, look up facts, buy goods
            and services, and communicate with others from around the world.
            It's important to PANORAH to help our customers retain their privacy
