              Information you have already provided us such as your name,
              address, phone number, and email address.
            </li>
            <li>
              Information you have updated, such as your preferences for
              receiving marketing information.
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            We use this information to help you more easily purchase products,
            download free software, and register your products. You can view and
            modify your personal profile by visiting the Profile Center.
